high_descs: Turn left and go to the small black table in the right corner.
Pick up the yellow knife on the table on the left.
Slice a half of the potato on the table.
Turn left and go to the right side of the white table.
Place the yellow knife on the table over the fork.
Turn right and go back to the black table with the sliced potato.
Pick up one slice of potato from the table.
Turn right and go across the kitchen to the white table in the right corner.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave on the top of the white table and take it out.
Turn around and go back to the small black table with sliced potato.
Place the heated potato slice on the table on the right of the salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated slice of potato next to the salt shaker on the black table.

high_descs: Turn around, walk across the room, then turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Turn around, then turn right to face the table.
Place the knife on the table,
Turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the piece of potato furthest to the right.
Turn around, walk across the room, turn left, walk until you hit the garbage can, turn right and walk until you hit the wall, then turn left to face the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the potato inside, close the door, microwave for two seconds, then remove the potato.
Turn left, walk across the room, turn left, walk across the room, then turn right and walk to the counter.
Place the cooked potato piece to the right of the salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Cook a piece of potato and return it to the counter.

high_descs: Go to the small black table next to the kitchen counter
Pick up the knife from the table
Cut the potato on the table
Go to the white table
Place the knife on the table
Turn to the black table
Pick up a potato slice
Go to the microwave
Heat the potato slice
Go to the black table
Place the potato slice on the black table
anns.task_desc: Cut and heat a slice of potato
